products.title: Azurite Chenille Coral Pink Curtain
products.description: Their azurite chenille range consists of textured plains with a velour soft-feel finish. These soft coral pink curtains fuse a plush, luxury feel in a contemporary pink tone to create a on trend room feature that is bound to be noticed. These curtains are perfect to add richness and a splash of colour when paired with cool, contemporary greys. All their curtains are lovingly handmade within the uk.
